BT /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 66 360 Tm (- Administrative access must be used only for project operations, maintenance,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 66 346 Tm (  debugging, or approved academic review.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 66 332 Tm (- Sensitive user data must not be copied, shared, or exported outside the project) Tj ET
